ou and your experience with us is memorable.\r\n\r\nWhen you leave, may your journey home be safe and your business contacts profitable.\r\n\r\nWe are all travelers. From \'birth till death\' we travel between eternities. May the days you spent with us be pleasant for you, profitable for society, helpful for those you meet and a joy to those who know and love you best.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;','NLGS Mission Statement','','publish','open','closed','','nlgs-mission-statement','','','2013-08-08 12:51:32','2013-08-08 12:51:32','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?page_id=14',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2013-08-06 12:45:41','2013-08-06 12:45:41','<div>Because this event is a human interaction event to serve people and not solely a money making organization we hope that God will grant you relationships that foster, grow and serve your needs in the business world.\r\n\r\nMay this event be prosperous for all persons that attend, and, that it effectively serves your needs in this industry.\r\n\r\nMay the business that brought you our way prosper and every appointment you have and every message you receive add to your joy.\r\n\r\nMay our staff serve you in a manner that pleases you and your experience with us is memorable.\r\n\r\nWhen you leave, may your journey home be safe and your business contacts profitable.\r\n\r\nWe are all travelers. From \'birth till death\' we travel between eternities. May the days you spent with us be pleasant for you, profitable for society, helpful for those you meet and a joy to those who know and love you best.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','NLGS Mission Statement','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-v1','','','2013-08-06 12:45:41','2013-08-06 12:45:41','',14,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=15',0,'revision','',0),(16,1,'2013-08-06 12:46:06','2013-08-06 12:46:06','','Our Mission Statement','NLGS Mission Statement','publish','open','open','','16','','','2013-08-08 15:12:39','2013-08-08 15:12:39','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=16',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(17,1,'2013-08-06 12:46:28','2013-08-06 12:46:28','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-08-06 12:46:28','2013-08-06 12:46:28','',2,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=17',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2013-08-06 14:56:16','2013-08-06 14:56:16','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/WhyAttend.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"Why Attend the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show?\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/WhyAttend.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a Buyer...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">This is Not Your Average Trade Show!</span></strong> The National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is not the trade show you\'re used to!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>You save time with our signature pre-set appointment format.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You select the products you want to see, eliminating unnecessary appointments.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Vendors bring the products to you at your private conference table.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Presentations will be personalized with your requirements. </strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Enjoy networking opportunities, events, product displays and new product prototype reviews, too!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a vendor...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">An Event with Guaranteed Results!</span></strong>\r\nThe National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is best described as \"speed-dating for Lawn and Garden products!\"</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There\'s <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no booth</span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no additional set up expenses.</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>Here, <strong>you are in the drivers seat</strong>. Instead of standing in a booth, you move from buyer to buyer according to a guaranteed, pre-set appointment schedule.</li>\r\n	<li>No more waiting and wondering if you\'ll see the right buyer. As a Vendor at the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show, you\'ll meet one on one with real decision makers who will give you a yes or a no on the spot! <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/satisfactionguarantee\">Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</a></span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>We are so confident in the appointment format, that we guarantee you will meet buyers on a pre-set, one-on-one, appointment basis. <strong>No other trade event in the industry can offer you this!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n\r\n</div>','Why Attend the National Lawn & Garden Show?','','publish','open','closed','','why-attend-the-national-lawn-garden-show','','','2013-08-08 12:53:20','2013-08-08 12:53:20','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),(19,1,'2013-08-06 14:56:16','2013-08-06 14:56:16','<div class=\"content\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/WhyAttend.png\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a Buyer...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">This is Not Your Average Trade Show!</span></strong> The National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is not the trade show you\'re used to!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>You save time with our signature pre-set appointment format.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You select the products you want to see, eliminating unnecessary appointments.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Vendors bring the products to you at your private conference table.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Presentations will be personalized with your requirements. </strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Enjoy networking opportunities, events, product displays and new product prototype reviews, too!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a vendor...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">An Event with Guaranteed Results!</span></strong>\r\nThe National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is best described as \"speed-dating for Lawn and Garden products!\"</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There\'s <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no booth</span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no additional set up expenses.</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>Here, <strong>you are in the drivers seat</strong>. Instead of standing in a booth, you move from buyer to buyer according to a guaranteed, pre-set appointment schedule.</li>\r\n	<li>No more waiting and wondering if you\'ll see the right buyer. As a Vendor at the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show, you\'ll meet one on one with real decision makers who will give you a yes or a no on the spot! <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/satisfactionguarantee\">Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</a></span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>We are so confident in the appointment format, that we guarantee you will meet buyers on a pre-set, one-on-one, appointment basis. <strong>No other trade event in the industry can offer you this!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n\r\n</div>','Why Attend the National Lawn & Garden Show?','','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-v1','','','2013-08-06 14:56:16','2013-08-06 14:56:16','',18,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=19',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2013-08-06 14:57:16','2013-08-06 14:57:16','','Why Attend?','Why Attend the National Lawn & Garden Show?','publish','open','open','','20','','','2013-08-08 15:12:39','2013-08-08 15:12:39','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=20',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(21,1,'2013-08-06 14:58:50','2013-08-06 14:58:50','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ApptFormat.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-135\" alt=\"Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ApptFormat.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\nGuaranteed Pre-Set, Scheduled Appointments are the specialty of the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show and are what sets the event apart from other trade events. High volume buyers are matched with quality vendors based on common product interests resulting in thousands of qualified appointments. Ample time is reserved for buyers to visit the Point of Purchase (POP) Showcase and New Product/Prototype areas.\r\n<h3>Who participates?</h3>\r\nNLGS Appointments are exclusive and open only to qualified decision-making buyers and vendors. Vendors must have high volume manufacturing capabilities, possess the ability to distribute nationally, and be prepared to entertain international interest. Buyers are high volume buyers with extensive purchasing authority and each buying company must meet minimum sales volume or store count to qualify and attend.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 270px;\">- Buying Groups</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 250px;\">- Catalogs and Direct Mail Companies</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Co-ops</td>\r\n<td>- Department Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- E-commerce</td>\r\n<td>- Farm &amp; Fleet Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Wholesale Distributors</td>\r\n<td>- Liquidators</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Regional Retail Chains</td>\r\n<td>- Television and Home Shopping</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Multi-unit Independent Garden Centers</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>\r\nHow do the appointments work?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Buyers select the product categories they are interested in, which determines the vendors they will see.</li>\r\n	<li>Vendors select their product categories, which determines which buyers they match. Closer to the event vendors\r\nchoose which \"matching\" buyers they would like to see and can sort the buyers by importance and priority.</li>\r\n	<li>Appointments are scheduled in advance by proprietary automated appointment software. This means buyers and\r\nsellers will only see companies that match with their respective product categories.</li>\r\n	<li>Appointment schedules are distributed to buyers and sellers at the event.</li>\r\n	<li>Buyers are assigned conference tables while vendors follow their pre-set schedule and move from table to table.</li>\r\n	<li>Each appointment is 10 minutes in length and automated voice prompts keep the appointments running smoothly.</li>\r\n	<li>If a buyer and a vendor wish to meet longer, \"Bonus Time\" is set aside each day to facilitate a second (or third) meeting.</li>\r\n	<li>NLGS\'s software powered by Controlled Marketing Conferences, Inc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments:','','publish','open','open','','pre-set-scheduled-appointments','','','2013-08-08 12:55:05','2013-08-08 12:55:05','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?page_id=21',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2013-08-06 14:58:50','2013-08-06 14:58:50','<div class=\"content\">\r\n    <img src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/ApptFormat.png\">\r\n\r\n<p>Guaranteed Pre-Set, Scheduled Appointments are the specialty of the National Lawn & Garden Show and are what sets the event apart from other trade events. High volume buyers are matched with quality vendors based on common product interests resulting in thousands of qualified appointments. Ample time is reserved for buyers to visit the Point of Purchase (POP) Showcase and New Product/Prototype areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>\r\nWho participates?\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNLGS Appointments are exclusive and open only to qualified decision-making buyers and vendors. Vendors must have high volume manufacturing capabilities, possess the ability to distribute nationally, and be prepared to entertain international interest. Buyers are high volume buyers with extensive purchasing authority and each buying company must meet minimum sales volume or store count to qualify and attend.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width:270px;\">- Buying Groups</td>\r\n<td style=\"width:250px;\">- Catalogs and Direct Mail Companies</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Co-ops</td>\r\n<td>- Department Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- E-commerce</td>\r\n<td>- Farm & Fleet Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Wholesale Distributors</td>\r\n<td>- Liquidators</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Regional Retail Chains</td>\r\n<td>- Television and Home Shopping</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Multi-unit Independent Garden Centers</td><td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<H3>\r\nHow do the appointments work?\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Buyers select the product categories they are interested in, which determines the vendors they will see.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Vendors select their product categories, which determines which buyers they match. Closer to the event vendors\r\nchoose which \"matching\" buyers they would like to see and can sort the buyers by importance and priority.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Appointments are scheduled in advance by proprietary automated appointment software. This means buyers and\r\nsellers will only see companies that match with their respective product categories.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Appointment schedules are distributed to buyers and sellers at the event.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Buyers are assigned conference tables while vendors follow their pre-set schedule and move from table to table.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Each appointment is 10 minutes in length and automated voice prompts keep the appointments running smoothly.</li> \r\n\r\n<li>If a buyer and a  vendor wish to meet longer, \"Bonus Time\" is set aside each day to facilitate a second (or third) meeting. </li>\r\n\r\n<li>NLGS\'s software powered by Controlled Marketing Conferences, Inc.</li>\r\n</ul>  </div>\r\n\r\n  </div>		','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments:','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-v1','','','2013-08-06 14:58:50','2013-08-06 14:58:50','',21,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=22',0,'revision','',0),(23,1,'2013-08-06 14:59:09','2013-08-06 14:59:09','','Appointment Format','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments:','publish','open','open','','23','','','2013-08-08 15:12:39','2013-08-08 15:12:39','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=23',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(24,1,'2013-08-06 15:02:38','2013-08-06 15:02:38','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uplo