uyers we would not have met otherwise, professional and casual, great if you are new to the business.\" </em>\r\n<strong> Rubber Design by Rainbow</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Much more efficient and a better use of time than other events.\"</em>\r\n<strong> Generation Online</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Face to face contact with buyers, 10 minutes is just enough time.\"</em>\r\n<strong> Jagram S. A.</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Speed dating, effective, efficient. More efficient use of time and better ROI\" </em>\r\n<strong> Woodstock Chimes</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Definitely a must attend-very productive show. Easy access to a wide variety of buyers/companies.\" </em>\r\n<strong> Zenith Innovation, LLC</strong>\r\n<h3>What are previous <em>BUYERS</em> saying about NLGS?</h3>\r\n<strong><em>SKH stated,</em></strong> \"This is an easy way to find \'Diamonds in the Rough\' and to be on the cutting edge of this industry\"\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Armstrong Garden Center</em></strong> commented that this is an \"excellent format, makes the most of initial time with little waste.\"\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Aco Hardware</em></strong> has said, \"A great way to meet a lot of vendors in a short period of time.\"\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Commerce Distributors</em></strong> said, \"Amazing what can be accomplished in 10 minutes.\"\r\n\r\nExcellent, unmatched efficient use of time! Second to none!!\" said <em><strong>Meyer Seed of Baltimore</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<em><strong>The Greatest Gift,</strong></em> stated \"Saw many new products without walking a huge show.\"\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Plow &amp; Hearth</strong></em> \"Much more interesting and focused, I don\'t feel that I missed finding a good product\"\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Earl May</strong></em> said, \"A show focused more on making contacts than walking booths\" and \"I was able to help a vendor with packaging ideas that eventually helped me sell more of their product\"\r\n\r\n\"One of a kind---A place to be and a place to be seen!\" <em><strong> Groupex</strong></e