 any additional questions can be answered\r\nby the event management. This service is yours simply by asking and is\r\ncomplimentary!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\";>For mentors contact us at 888-316-0226 or 719-488-0226 or you may\r\n<a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/contact\">email us</a> to get paired up with a mentor\r\nspecifically for you.</p>','Buyer Mentor Program','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2013-08-07 03:31:47','2013-08-07 03:31:47','',62,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=63',0,'revision','',0),(64,1,'2013-08-07 03:32:31','2013-08-07 03:32:31','<a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/BuyerVIA.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-159\" alt=\"Buyers VIA\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/BuyerVIA.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe VIA event is a great way to relax and enjoy time with a select group of vendors in a relaxed social atmosphere. VIA events are generally held off site in a unique setting or location with dinner and cocktails throughout the evening. NO selling takes place at this function and is purely social in nature. We encourage all registered buyers to attend VIA events. This is a great way to further develop business relationships with current or new companies you are considering doing business with. See you at this years VIA event!!!!\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/galleryVIA\">VIA photo gallery!</a>','Buyer VIA','','publish','open','closed','','buyer-via','','','2013-08-08 13:14:05','2013-08-08 13:14:05','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?page_id=64',0,'page','',0),(65,1,'2013-08-07 03:32:31','2013-08-07 03:32:31','<img src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/BuyerVIA.png\">\r\n\r\n<p>The VIA event is a great way to relax and enjoy time with a select group of vendors in a relaxed social atmosphere. VIA events are generally held off site in a unique setting or location with dinner and cocktails t