 to a guaranteed, pre-set appointment schedule.</li>\n	<li>No more waiting and wondering if you\'ll see the right buyer. As a Vendor at the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show, you\'ll meet one on one with real decision makers who will give you a yes or a no on the spot! <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/satisfactionguarantee\">Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</a></span></strong></li>\n	<li>We are so confident in the appointment format, that we guarantee you will meet buyers on a pre-set, one-on-one, appointment basis. <strong>No other trade event in the industry can offer you this!</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\n\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\n\n</div>','Why Attend the National Lawn & Garden Show?','','inherit','open','open','','18-autosave-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:53:08','2013-08-08 12:53:08','',18,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=133',0,'revision','',0),(134,1,'2013-08-08 12:53:20','2013-08-08 12:53:20','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/WhyAttend.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-132\" alt=\"Why Attend the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show?\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/WhyAttend.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a Buyer...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">This is Not Your Average Trade Show!</span></strong> The National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is not the trade show you\'re used to!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>You save time with our signature pre-set appointment format.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>You select the products you want to see, eliminating unnecessary appointments.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Vendors bring the products to you at your private conference table.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Presentations will be personalized with your requirements. </strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Enjoy networking opportunities, events, product displays and new product prototype reviews, too!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As a vendor...</em></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">An Event with Guaranteed Results!</span></strong>\r\nThe National Lawn &amp; Garden Show is best described as \"speed-dating for Lawn and Garden products!\"</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There\'s <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no booth</span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">no additional set up expenses.</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>Here, <strong>you are in the drivers seat</strong>. Instead of standing in a booth, you move from buyer to buyer according to a guaranteed, pre-set appointment schedule.</li>\r\n	<li>No more waiting and wondering if you\'ll see the right buyer. As a Vendor at the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show, you\'ll meet one on one with real decision makers who will give you a yes or a no on the spot! <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/satisfactionguarantee\">Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</a></span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>We are so confident in the appointment format, that we guarantee you will meet buyers on a pre-set, one-on-one, appointment basis. <strong>No other trade event in the industry can offer you this!</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/testimonials\">Click to see TESTIMONIALS</a>\r\n\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/gallery\">Appointments photo gallery!</a>\r\n\r\n</div>','Why Attend the National Lawn & Garden Show?','','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:53:20','2013-08-08 12:53:20','',18,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=134',0,'revision','',0),(135,1,'2013-08-08 12:54:07','2013-08-08 12:54:07','','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments','','inherit','open','open','','apptformat','','','2013-08-08 12:54:07','2013-08-08 12:54:07','',21,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ApptFormat.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(136,1,'2013-08-08 12:54:49','2013-08-08 12:54:49','<div class=\"content\"></div>\n<div class=\"content\">\nGuaranteed Pre-Set, Scheduled Appointments are the specialty of the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show and are what sets the event apart from other trade events. High volume buyers are matched with quality vendors based on common product interests resulting in thousands of qualified appointments. Ample time is reserved for buyers to visit the Point of Purchase (POP) Showcase and New Product/Prototype areas.\n<h3>Who participates?</h3>\nNLGS Appointments are exclusive and open only to qualified decision-making buyers and vendors. Vendors must have high volume manufacturing capabilities, possess the ability to distribute nationally, and be prepared to entertain international interest. Buyers are high volume buyers with extensive purchasing authority and each buying company must meet minimum sales volume or store count to qualify and attend.\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 270px;\">- Buying Groups</td>\n<td style=\"width: 250px;\">- Catalogs and Direct Mail Companies</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>- Co-ops</td>\n<td>- Department Stores</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>- E-commerce</td>\n<td>- Farm &amp; Fleet Stores</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>- Wholesale Distributors</td>\n<td>- Liquidators</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>- Regional Retail Chains</td>\n<td>- Television and Home Shopping</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>- Multi-unit Independent Garden Centers</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>\nHow do the appointments work?</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Buyers select the product categories they are interested in, which determines the vendors they will see.</li>\n	<li>Vendors select their product categories, which determines which buyers they match. Closer to the event vendors\nchoose which \"matching\" buyers they would like to see and can sort the buyers by importance and priority.</li>\n	<li>Appointments are scheduled in advance by proprietary automated appointment software. This means buyers and\nsellers will only see companies that match with their respective product categories.</li>\n	<li>Appointment schedules are distributed to buyers and sellers at the event.</li>\n	<li>Buyers are assigned conference tables while vendors follow their pre-set schedule and move from table to table.</li>\n	<li>Each appointment is 10 minutes in length and automated voice prompts keep the appointments running smoothly.</li>\n	<li>If a buyer and a vendor wish to meet longer, \"Bonus Time\" is set aside each day to facilitate a second (or third) meeting.</li>\n	<li>NLGS\'s software powered by Controlled Marketing Conferences, Inc.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments:','','inherit','open','open','','21-autosave-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:54:49','2013-08-08 12:54:49','',21,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=136',0,'revision','',0),(137,1,'2013-08-08 12:55:05','2013-08-08 12:55:05','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ApptFormat.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-135\" alt=\"Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ApptFormat.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\nGuaranteed Pre-Set, Scheduled Appointments are the specialty of the National Lawn &amp; Garden Show and are what sets the event apart from other trade events. High volume buyers are matched with quality vendors based on common product interests resulting in thousands of qualified appointments. Ample time is reserved for buyers to visit the Point of Purchase (POP) Showcase and New Product/Prototype areas.\r\n<h3>Who participates?</h3>\r\nNLGS Appointments are exclusive and open only to qualified decision-making buyers and vendors. Vendors must have high volume manufacturing capabilities, possess the ability to distribute nationally, and be prepared to entertain international interest. Buyers are high volume buyers with extensive purchasing authority and each buying company must meet minimum sales volume or store count to qualify and attend.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 270px;\">- Buying Groups</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 250px;\">- Catalogs and Direct Mail Companies</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Co-ops</td>\r\n<td>- Department Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- E-commerce</td>\r\n<td>- Farm &amp; Fleet Stores</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Wholesale Distributors</td>\r\n<td>- Liquidators</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Regional Retail Chains</td>\r\n<td>- Television and Home Shopping</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- Multi-unit Independent Garden Centers</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>\r\nHow do the appointments work?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Buyers select the product categories they are interested in, which determines the vendors they will see.</li>\r\n	<li>Vendors select their product categories, which determines which buyers they match. Closer to the event vendors\r\nchoose which \"matching\" buyers they would like to see and can sort the buyers by importance and priority.</li>\r\n	<li>Appointments are scheduled in advance by proprietary automated appointment software. This means buyers and\r\nsellers will only see companies that match with their respective product categories.</li>\r\n	<li>Appointment schedules are distributed to buyers and sellers at the event.</li>\r\n	<li>Buyers are assigned conference tables while vendors follow their pre-set schedule and move from table to table.</li>\r\n	<li>Each appointment is 10 minutes in length and automated voice prompts keep the appointments running smoothly.</li>\r\n	<li>If a buyer and a vendor wish to meet longer, \"Bonus Time\" is set aside each day to facilitate a second (or third) meeting.</li>\r\n	<li>NLGS\'s software powered by Controlled Marketing Conferences, Inc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Pre-Set Scheduled Appointments:','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:55:05','2013-08-08 12:55:05','',21,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=137',0,'revision','',0),(138,1,'2013-08-08 12:55:51','2013-08-08 12:55:51','','Overview Point of Purchase Showcase','','inherit','open','open','','o_pop','','','2013-08-08 12:55:51','2013-08-08 12:55:51','',24,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/O_pop.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(139,1,'2013-08-08 12:56:14','2013-08-08 12:56:14','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/O_pop.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-138\" alt=\"Overview Point of Purchase Showcase\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/O_pop.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\nThe Point of Purchase \"POP\" Showcase gives vendors the chance to display products, packaging and POP material in a retail setting. No\r\ntraditional tradeshow backdrops are allowed. No utilities are available in this area. Buyers spend time in the Point of Purchase Showcase\r\nin preparation for appointments. Buyers have continuous access to view products in this area throughout the event.\r\n<h3>How are products displayed in the Point of Purchase Showcase?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Point of Purchase Showcase:</strong> Up to three 2\' x 2\' POP spaces can be reserved for each vendor. Floor or table top space is\r\navailable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>How much does A Point of Purchase Display cost?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Three 2\' x 2\' spaces are included with vendor registration. Additional POP space can be purchased for $100 per additional 2\'x2\'\r\nspace.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nView our <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/galleryEvents\">POP photo gallery!</a>\r\n\r\n</div>','Point of Purchase Showcase (POP)','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:56:14','2013-08-08 12:56:14','',24,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=139',0,'revision','',0),(140,1,'2013-08-08 12:57:02','2013-08-08 12:57:02','','Overview New Product Review','','inherit','open','open','','prototype','','','2013-08-08 12:57:02','2013-08-08 12:57:02','',26,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/prototype.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(141,1,'2013-08-08 12:57:19','2013-08-08 12:57:19','<div class=\"content\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/prototype.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-140\" alt=\"Overview New Product Review\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/prototype.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Enjoy the rare opportunity to have buyers preview and evaluate your newest products in the event\'s secure Prototype Room.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Here buyers share their opinions and written comments with you according to uniqueness, pricing, packaging and many other factors. This provides an invaluable source of information that helps shape the future design and production of lawn &amp; garden products. Buyers also select a product for \"Best of Show Award\". Vendors will receive the buyer\'s written feedback at the end of the event. The area is accessible throughout the event for buyers only. The set-up is identical to the Point of Purchase (POP) area.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How much does it cost to display in the New Product Prototype Preview?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1 Product Entry: $250</li>\r\n	<li>2 Product Entries: $350</li>\r\n	<li>3 Product Entries $450</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','New Product/Prototype Review','','inherit','open','open','','26-revision-v1','','','2013-08-08 12:57:19','2013-08-08 12:57:19','',26,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=141',0,'revision','',0),(142,1,'2013-08-08 12:58:13','2013-08-08 12:58:13','','Overview Testimonials','','inherit','open','open','','testimonials','','','2013-08-08 12:58:13','2013-08-08 12:58:13','',28,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/testimonials.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(144,1,'2013-08-08 13:04:00','2013-08-08 13:04:00','','Overview Previous Attendees','','inherit','open','open','','prevattend','','','2013-08-08 13:04:00','2013-08-08 13:04:00','',33,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/PrevAttend.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(146,1,'2013-08-08 13:05:25','2013-08-08 13:05:25','','Overview Schedule','','inherit','open','open','','schedule','','','2013-08-08 13:05:25','2013-08-08 13:05:25','',35,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/schedule.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(148,1,'2013-08-08 13:07:11','2013-08-08 13:07:11','','Overview Travel Info','','inherit','open','open','','travel','','','2013-08-08 13:07:11','2013-08-08 13:07:11','',37,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(149,1,'2013-08-08 13:07:29','2013-08-08 13:07:29','<a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-148\" alt=\"Overview Travel Info\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"10\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"175px\" height=\"95px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/nlgshow_core/images/NLGS-Logo.gif\" border=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">\nThe National Lawn &amp; Garden Show\nwill be held June 11-13, 2013\nCrowne Plaza Chicago O’Hare Hotel &amp;\nConference Center, Rosemont, IL</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">ARRIVAL &amp; DEPARTURE INFORMATION</span></strong>\nVendors will need to make your airfare arrangements to arrive at the hotel no later than 1:00 PM on Monday, (Buyers may arrive as late as 3PM) June 10, 2013. Your appointments could last until 11:30 AM on Thursday, June 13th, so please book your return flight accordingly. <strong>You may schedule your return flight anytime after 1:00 PM</strong>, Thursday, June 13th. Appointments will run June 11th – 13th for all NLGS buyers and vendors.\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Check-in &amp; P.O.P &amp; Prototype Set-up:</span></strong>\nCheck-in and POP/Prototype Display set-up will start at 10:00 AM and end at 4:00 PM on Monday, June 10th. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">POP &amp; Prototype set up must be completed by 4:00 PM, as buyers will have access to preview the POP area and evaluate the Prototype area.</span> No exceptions please!\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Hotel Accommodations: Crowne Plaza Chicago O’Hare Hotel &amp; Conference Center, Rosemont, IL</span>:</strong>\n5440 North River Road, Rosemont, IL 60018. <a href=\"http://www.crowneplazaohare.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.crowneplazaohare.com</a> Register by clicking the link:\n<a href=\"https://resweb.passkey.com/Resweb.do?mode=welcome_ei_new&amp;eventID=9943616\" target=\"_blank\">https://resweb.passkey.com/Resweb.do?mode=welcome_ei_new&amp;eventID=9943616</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\">Booking Code:NLF you will get a confirmation number upon completion of your reservation, or by calling 877-337-5793 or central reservations at 843-760-5839 (Toll Free). The negotiated room rate is $135.00 single or double occupancy. You must mention the “National Lawn &amp; Garden Show” Booking code: NLF to get the discounted room rate. Please ask the hotel about its reservation &amp; cancellation policies. Please call by May 31, 2013, 8 PM CST to guarantee the discounted rate. After this date please call 888-233-9534 and we will make every effort to secure the discount, however prevailing rates will apply and rates are as high as $220 per night. <strong>There are several events taking place in our timeframe at the Rosemont Convention Center so rooms will be scarce, please reserve early. </strong></p>\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Complimentary Hotel Shuttle Service to/from O’Hare Airport</span></strong>:\nThe hotel is 10 minutes from O’Hare airport. The Crowne Plaza O\'Hare provides a 24 hour complimentary airport shuttle to and from O’Hare International Airport. Crowne Plaza’s pickup location for domestic travelers in O\'Hare is at Door 2 of the Shuttle Bus Center. International travelers please use the courtesy phones in the baggage area to contact the hotel to schedule a pick-up. From Midway Airport use rental car or book with private limo or cab as no complimentary service is available.\n\nDiscount Car Rental rates: We have negotiated special rates with Thrifty Car Rental.  The special code is valid throughout the year and nationwide.  Use Corporate Discount Code 004M002073 at <a href=\"http://www.thrifty.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.thrifty.com</a> or call 1-800-THRIFTY (847-4389) (US &amp; Canada) or 1-918-669-2168 (outside US and Canada). Or go to <a href=\"http://www.thrifty.com/reservations/index.aspx?corpnum=004M002073\" target=\"_blank\">www.thrifty.com/reservations/index.aspx?corpnum=004M002073</a>\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Driving Directions</span></strong><strong>: </strong>\n<strong>From O’Hare Airport.</strong> Head East on I-190, for 2 miles to River Road. Turn right on River Road and proceed down to 5440 N. River Road, directly across from the convention center.\n<strong>From the East (Chicago).</strong> Take I90 West to 190 (O’Hare exit) continue 15 miles to River Road exit. Turn right on River Road and proceed to 5440 N. River Road directly across from the convention center.\n<strong>From the West (Rockford).</strong> Take I90 East to Chicago. Exit on Cumberland Road North. Go right on Cumberland, 2 blocks to 1st light (Higgins/Rt.72). Go left on Higgins and proceed 1 mile to River Road. Go left on River Road and proceed to 5440 N. River Road directly across from the Convention Center.\n<strong>From the South (Indiana).</strong> Take 294 North (Wisconsin) and follow signs to 190 (O’Hare exit). Take 190 to River Road (1st light). Go right on River Road and proceed to 5440 N. River Road directly across from the Convention Center.\n<strong>From the North (Wisconsin).</strong> Take 294 South to 190 East, follow signs to O’Hare. Pay at toll. Stay in the right lane. Exit Mannheim Road South. Get back on the highway and follow signs to Chicago. Exit River Road South. Turn Right. Hotel is on the right side, approximately 2 blocks down.\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Opening Reception</span>:</strong>\nPlease note that all participants are expected to be at the Hotel on Monday, June 10th, at 6:00 PM for Dinner Reception and Orientation Meeting.\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Emergency Contact:</span></strong>\nAppointments will begin at 8:30 AM on Tuesday, June 11th, and will conclude on Thursday June 13th at 11:30 AM. Please fax emergency contact information to 719-488-8168 in case we need to contact you during the event.\n\n</div>','NLGS Venue & Travel Info.','','inherit','open','open','','37-autosave-v1','','','2013-08-08 13:07:29','2013-08-08 13:07:29','',37,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=149',0,'revision','',0),(150,1,'2013-08-08 13:07:43','2013-08-08 13:07:43','','NLGS Color Logo','','inherit','open','open','','nlgs-logo','','','2013-08-08 13:07:43','2013-08-08 13:07:43','',37,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/NLGS-Logo.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(151,1,'2013-08-08 13:08:01','2013-08-08 13:08:01'