3-08-08 14:07:30','2013-08-08 14:07:30','<img src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/thanks.png\">\r\n\r\n<p>The Board of Directors in conjunction with NLGS has initiated for 2013 and beyond a vendor\r\ncompany loyalty discount program for companies who have consistently attended NLGS\r\nsince its inception in 1995. This is a \"company\" attendance discount and not a \"personal\"\r\nattendance discount, as people move from company to company. NLGS would like\r\nto \"give back\" to loyal supporting companies who have attended throughout the years. We\r\nsincerely appreciate your loyalty to NLGS and trust our event has increased your company’s\r\npresence in the Lawn &amp; Garden Marketplace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For vendor companies who have attended the event for at least three (3) years since 1995,\r\nNLGS is offering a graduated discount to the current registration fee. The more years that\r\nan individual company has attended the event the higher the discount is and the more\r\ncomplimentary services your company will receive. Please contact our office at 888-316-0226 or <a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/contact\" target=\"_blank\">email us</a> to find out if your company qualifies for any loyalty\r\ndiscounts. Years attended are solely verified by NLGS attendance records.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loyalty discounts only apply to next year’s event if the company registers by December 31st\r\nand a $500 deposit is made to secure your scheduling position. The Board will not deviate\r\nfrom this policy or registration deadline dates. In addition, any early registration discounts\r\nwill also be deducted from the registration fee when the registration is post marked or web\r\nreceived by close of business December 31st of the year prior to the event.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Discounts begin after 3 years of attendance and increase as your company continuously\r\nattends. Discounts range from at 5% to 25% off current registration fees with select\r\ncomplimentary services included at the 25% level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Companies exhibiting over 15 years with NLGS receive a <strong>permanently locked registration\r\nfee</strong> with priority scheduling options, additional complimentary services and complimentary\r\nVIA participation and sponsorship!! When your company reaches the 20 year attendance\r\nmark, <strong>all fees are waived for that year!!!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We sincerely appreciate your loyalty to the National Lawn&amp; Garden Show, and trust your\r\nbusiness has grown and benefitted from consistently attending the event.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold;\">Thank you for your patronage over the years!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><i><a href=\"http://www.nlgshow.com/contact\">Email NLGS</a> now to confirm loyalty discount!</i></p>','NLGS Company Loyalty Discounts','','inherit','open','open','','113-revision-v1','','','2013-08-08 14:07:30','2013-08-08 14:07:30','',113,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=181',0,'revision','',0),(182,1,'2013-08-08 14:08:07','2013-08-08 14:08:07','','Thank You!','','inherit','open','open','','thanks','','','2013-08-08 14:08:07','2013-08-08 14:08:07','',113,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/thanks.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(183,1,'2013-08-08 14:08:20','2013-08-08 14:08:20','<a href=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/thanks.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-182\" alt=\"Thank You!\" src=\"http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/thanks.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"221\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Board of Directors in conjunction with NLGS has initiated for 2013 and beyond a vendor\r\ncompany loyalty discount program for companies who have consistently attended NLGS\r\nsince its inception in 1995. This is a \"company\" attendance discount and not a \"personal\"\r\nattendance discount, as people move from company to company. NLGS would like\r\nto \"give back\" to loyal supporting companies who have 